com.nestedbird.modules.formparser

Class ParameterMapParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nestedbird.modules.formparser.ParameterMapParser

  • public class ParameterMapParser
extends java.lang.Object
    The ParameterMapParser processes the payload from a form submission. It converts the string array to a JSONObject with all children objects/arrays nested.

    The instanced version of ParameterMapVersion serves as offering an abstraction over JSONObject
